-- Argentine Raises Pensioners Payments 15.18%, Fernandez Says
-- B y   P a b l o   G o n z a l e z
-- 2013-01-28T23:17:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-28/argentine-raises-pensioners-payments-15-18-fernandez-says.html
Argentine retirees will receive a
15.18 percent increase to their minimum pension payments,
President  Cristina Fernandez de Kirchner  said in a speech in
Buenos Aires today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
